OL,3,CWelsh firm fined #2.2 million after
OL,4,Cworker killed in conveyor crush
OL,6,FA builders' merchant has been fined
OL,7,Fmore than #2 million after a worker
OL,8,Fwas crushed to death by a three-tonne
OL,9,Fpallet of timber.
OL,11,FPaul Coulson, 56, died after a
OL,12,Fcolleague started a conveyor not
OL,13,Frealising Mr Coulson had climbed
OL,14,Finside it, the Health and Safety
OL,15,FExecutive (HSE) said.
OL,17,FThe incident happened on May 22 2024
OL,18,Fat Herringswell Sawmills, a site in
OL,19,FBury St Edmunds in Suffolk operated by
OL,20,FHuws Gray Limited.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
