PN,46502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774868573
OL,3,CWelsh firm fined #2.2 million after
OL,4,Cworker killed in conveyor crush
OL,6,FMr Coulson, a labourer, had been
OL,7,Ftasked with removing plastic packaging
OL,8,Ffrom pallets of timber before they
OL,9,Fcould be processed at the mill.
OL,11,FHe had climbed within the framework of
OL,12,Fthe conveyor to access some of the
OL,13,Fpackaging, but another operative, who
OL,14,Fcould not see Mr Coulson from his
OL,15,Flocation, started the conveyor, which
OL,16,Fresulted in the pack of timber moving
OL,17,Fforward and colliding with him, the
OL,18,FHSE said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774868573
OL,3,CWelsh firm fined #2.2 million after
OL,4,Cworker killed in conveyor crush
OL,6,FThe operative, who could see that the
OL,7,Fpack of timber was not moving along
OL,8,Fthe conveyor as it should, reversed it
OL,9,Fbefore changing its direction, this
OL,10,Fresulted in the pack of timber moving
OL,11,Fforwards again, colliding with Mr
OL,12,FCoulson a second time, the HSE added.
OL,14,FMr Coulson died at the scene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
