PN,46506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774868573
OL,3,CWelsh firm fined #2.2 million after
OL,4,Cworker killed in conveyor crush
OL,6,FHuws Gray Limited based in Llangefni,
OL,7,FAnglesey, Wales, pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fbreaching the Health and Safety at
OL,9,FWork etc Act 1974 Section 2(1) and was
OL,10,Ffined #2.2 million and ordered to pay
OL,11,Ffull costs of #9,929 at Chelmsford
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday.
OL,14,FHSE inspector Joanne Williams said:
OL,15,F"This was a staggering failure that
OL,16,Fhas cost a man his life and robbed a
OL,17,Ffamily of their loved one, and the
OL,18,Fscale of the fine handed down reflects
OL,19,Fthe gravity of this case.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
