CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774868573
OL,3,CWelsh firm fined #2.2 million after
OL,4,Cworker killed in conveyor crush
OL,6,F"All companies, regardless of their
OL,7,Fsize, must follow the hierarchy of
OL,8,Fcontrol for guarding dangerous parts
OL,9,Fwithin work equipment.
OL,11,F"Our investigation revealed that in
OL,12,Fthis case, Huws Gray Ltd chose to
OL,13,Fcontrol a serious risk through
OL,14,Finstruction alone ` instead of putting
OL,15,Fproper safeguarding measures in place.
OL,17,F"This meant employees were able to
OL,18,Faccess a danger area, with tragic
OL,19,Fconsequences.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
