CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774868573
OL,3,CWelsh firm fined #2.2 million after
OL,4,Cworker killed in conveyor crush
OL,6,F"Had Huws Gray Ltd taken robust action
OL,7,Fwhen they became aware of the problem,
OL,8,FPaul Coulson would be alive today.
OL,10,F"Our thoughts will always remain with
OL,11,Fhis family and friends for the loss
OL,12,Fthey have suffered."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@TO]
